rComments: The worst prof I've seen in ELG so far. Fortunately I barely passed but half of the class either dropped out or failed. This professor enjoys teaching and is respectful and open-minded. The midterms and final exam varied quite a bit in terms of difficulty - some were easy; some were hard.

Glad that i'll never see him again.
